title: Lesnar returns for the Universal Title Match Contract Signing with Reigns: SmackDown, Oct. 15, 202..
author: WWE
description:
Prior to the Universal Title showdown against Roman Reigns at WWE Crown Jewel, Brock Lesnar participates in a tense contract signing with The Head of the Table and Paul Heyman. Catch WWE action on Peacock, WWE Network, FOX, USA Network, Sony India and more.
